                "invention-title": [
                    "High-quality salt production process for synergistically trapping carbon dioxide in flue gas by chemical adsorption method",
                    "化学吸附法协同捕集烟气中二氧化碳的高质盐生产工艺"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a high-quality salt production process for cooperatively capturing carbon dioxide in flue gas by a chemical adsorption method, which comprises the following steps: flue gas enters a first-stage spray tower and a second-stage spray tower through an induced draft fan, acid waste gases such as carbon dioxide, sulfur dioxide and hydrogen chloride in the waste gas are absorbed through alkali liquor spraying, and organic matters are removed through oxidation; meanwhile, sodium sulfite is oxidized into sodium sulfate, and low-carbon up-to-standard flue gas is discharged; alkali liquor enters from the lower part of the second-stage spray tower and is sprayed through a circulating pump, a compound oxidant enters from the lower part of the second-stage spray tower, the alkali liquor enters the first-stage tower through the second-stage spray tower and is sprayed, and a discharge hole is formed in the lower part of the first-stage spray tower and enters the reaction settling tank through a crystal slurry pump; circulating clear liquid in the settling tank to the first-stage spray tower, and performing dehydration and low-temperature drying on crystal slurry at the bottom of the settling tank to obtain a sodium bicarbonate product or performing high-temperature thermal desorption to obtain a sodium carbonate product."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开一种化学吸附法协同捕集烟气中二氧化碳的高质盐生产工艺，烟气通过引风机进入一级喷淋塔和二级喷淋塔，通过碱液喷淋将废气中的二氧化碳、二氧化硫及氯化氢等酸性废气吸收，再通过氧化将有机物去除，同时将亚硫酸钠氧化为硫酸钠，低碳达标烟气外排；碱液从二级喷淋塔下部进入，通过循环泵进行喷淋，复配氧化剂从二级喷淋塔下部进入，碱液再经二级喷淋塔进入一级塔喷淋，一级喷淋塔下部设有出料口，通过晶浆泵进入反应沉降罐，沉降罐清液循环至一级喷淋塔、沉降罐底部晶桨液再经脱水、低温烘干得到碳酸氢钠产品或高温热脱附得到碳酸钠产品。"
                }
            ]
